sys/memory/virtual/mapping.runa
Memory Mapping and mmap

This module provides virtual memory mapping functionality including
memory-mapped files, anonymous mappings, and virtual address space
management with cross-platform mmap interface support.
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

